{"type": "article", "id": 44959, "title": "挂历残忍起来，其实比谁都残忍｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-09-07T23:09:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 36763, "name": "DOIY"}, {"id": 30521, "name": "Instrmnt"}, {"id": 43894, "name": "papabubble"}, {"id": 40149, "name": "mousegraphics"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 159, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170907234126wd9QBS5U0lENfJPs.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Carpe Diem Calendar by DOIY</h3><p>2017 年已经过去大半，年初定下的计划完成得如何？还是已经在盘算明年的安排了？曾推出过 100 系列海报（我们此前介绍过其中的 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/38460.html\">to do list 款</a>）的西班牙创意品牌 <a href=\"https://doiydesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">DOIY</a> 延续了一贯的设计风格，早早地推出了可以一块块扯下的挂历 Carpe Diem。除了日期以外，每一块方格上还标有周数以及到年底的倒计时，鼓励你把握好时间（提醒你虚度了多少光阴）。这是它的<a href=\"https://doiydesign.com/product/carpe-diem-calendar-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 17.50 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234148U8bK51HAziMfr2CD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709072341487e4x2KA1Ofl9JdUs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709072341489rMUqELoWCjSFAlH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Oriboard by Zunik</h3><p>还记得那把像折纸一样、能够在四个尺寸间切换的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/33313.html\">量勺</a>吗？最近，由法国工业设计师 Yannick Hesch 创立的设计品牌 Zunik 带来了它的“放大版”——名为 Oriboard 的多功能砧板。它可以折叠成两种大小的容器，直接清洗、滤干食材。砧板的两个角落分别被设计成了研磨板和开瓶器，四周还留着浅浅的汁水收集槽，让料理变得更井然有序。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1932493634/oriboard-the-amazing-origami-multifunctional-cutti\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价为 19 欧元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234159IXi9yKMOCnxhdkrl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234159r2f1uTIZMAHzvKks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234159zbXGil6tnS9eq2x7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234159yfNEhYIot4UJ1lji.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>K Series by Instrmnt</h3><p>来自英国格拉斯哥的腕表品牌 Instrmnt 凭借简约的设计风格受到不少人的青睐，深受 20 世纪中期工业设计影响的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30022.html\">两位创始人</a>最近又带来了以 CMYK 印刷过程为灵感的 K 系列。三款的颜色分别对应了黑色（也就是 K，Key）31%、61% 以及 100% 的稀释程度，表带则由丁腈橡胶制成，具有良好的耐水性和耐磨性。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.instrmnt.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买，售价为 240 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234258DqSJlUutK7Z2BFAQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709072342582lXw4WqTJcNtAiRg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667901\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234258w6OSY0PIQgCKbpXs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667901\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709072342582WokdC5csZFIES1a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>耳のグミ by papabubble</h3><p>还没彻底送走夏天，日本的万圣节营销季就来了。以生产世界上最有趣的糖果为目标，源自西班牙巴塞罗那的手工糖果品牌 <a href=\"http://www.papabubble.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">papabubble</a> 自然也入乡随俗地开起了脑洞。继去年凭借“脑浆棉花糖”系列成为话题之后，他们最新的万圣节限定是这套耳朵形状的水果软糖。它们一共有 8 种口味可选，将从 9 月 16 日开始正式销售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234245iSGNjopICr1UMdfv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234245Cd0Hiv5gxEVPZRpK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Plier by Laurel Hwang</h3><p>为开放式环境打造的隔断也可以做到“百变”。最近，台湾设计师 Laurel Hwang 带来了这件名为 Plier 的多功能家具，借助隐藏在框架内的液压活塞，它可以在屏风和供 6 到 8 人使用的桌子间切换，让人们不再为特殊场合额外准备家具。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234404O2qf0o7dRn9Nb1HT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.831234\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234404q02pADXTSEoeWQFN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662893\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234404cswWEP1CyYpXbdNx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.829360\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mills of Saint George by mousegraphics</h3><p>来自塞浦路斯的创意机构 <a href=\"http://www.mousegraphics.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">mousegraphics</a> 最近为希腊面粉品牌 Mills of Saint George 更新了它的视觉形象，用朴实而具有亲和力的生面团替代了原先看起来有些老气的配图。这些生面团都是由雕塑家 Martha Foka 利用该品牌的面粉制作的：比如披萨面团直接表示披萨用面粉，小朋友造型的面团则代表了无麸质。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234220L15KEWdSFyD24OQp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.577535\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234221QxbdC1pqtfELYTGh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234220OHA0DQCoRyWBJdGh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.888571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170907234220NSHVJ4yw9Xm2DWn0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.888571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}